== Month of Yang Earth Rat ==
In a {{ill|Common Era|ja|и•њжЪ¶}} year whose last digit is 0 or 5 (when the Heavenly Stems are {{ill|K≈Н|ja|еЇЪ}} or {{ill|Otsu|ja|дєЩ}}), the month of {{ill|November|ja|11жЬИ}} is considered the Yang Earth Rat {{ill|month (calendar)|ja|жЬИ (жЪ¶)}}. However, the month referred to here may also be based on the {{ill|Old Calendar|ja|жЧІжЪ¶}} or on a seasonal month (from {{ill|Taisetsu|ja|е§ІйЫ™}} to the day before {{ill|Sh≈Нkan|ja|е∞ПеѓТ}}).

== Day of Yang Earth Rat ==
The selection of auspicious days for Yang Earth Rat is as follows.
=== Selected Day ===
The Yang Earth Rat day is the 5th day of {{ill|Tenp≈Нgure|ja|еНБжЦєжЪЃ}}.

