In a {{ill|Common Era|ja|и•њжЪ¶|12=draft|12=draft}} year whose last digit is 0 or 5 (when the Heavenly Stems are {{ill|K≈Н|ja|еЇЪ|1=Kanoe (еЇЪ)|12=draft|12=draft}} or {{ill|Otsu|ja|дєЩ|1=Kinoto (дєЩ)|12=draft|12=draft}}), the month of {{ill|November|ja|11жЬИ|12=draft|12=draft}} is considered the Yang Earth Rat {{ill|month (calendar)|ja|жЬИ (жЪ¶)|12=draft|12=draft}}. However, the month referred to here may also be based on the {{ill|Lunisolar|ja|жЧІжЪ¶|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|12=draft|12=draft}} or on a seasonal month (from {{ill|Taisetsu|ja|е§ІйЫ™|12=draft|12=draft}} to the day before {{ill|Sh≈Нkan|ja|е∞ПеѓТ|12=draft|12=draft}}).

