== Month of Yang Earth Rat ==
In a {{ill|Common Era|ja|и•њжЪ¶|1=Common Era|2=ja|3=и•њжЪ¶|4=zh|5=еЕђеЕГ|6=es|7=Era com√Їn|8=nl|9=Gangbare jaartelling|10=simple|11=Common Era|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Common Era|13=User:Immanuelle/Common Era|qq=}} year whose last digit is 0 or 5 (when the Heavenly Stems are {{ill|K≈Н|ja|еЇЪ|1=Kanoe (еЇЪ)|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/K≈Н|13=User:Immanuelle/Kanoe (еЇЪ)|qq=}} or {{ill|Otsu|ja|дєЩ|1=Kinoto (дєЩ)|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Otsu|13=User:Immanuelle/Kinoto (дєЩ)|qq=}}), the month of {{ill|November|ja|11жЬИ|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/November|qq=}} is considered the Yang Earth Rat {{ill|month (calendar)|ja|жЬИ (жЪ¶)|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/month (calendar)|qq=}}. However, the month referred to here may also be based on the {{ill|Lunisolar|ja|жЧІжЪ¶|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Lunisolar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}} or on a seasonal month (from {{ill|Taisetsu|ja|е§ІйЫ™|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Taisetsu|qq=}} to the day before {{ill|Sh≈Нkan|ja|е∞ПеѓТ|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sh≈Нkan|qq=}}).

