{{Sexagenary cycle comprehensive|qq=}}
'''Yang Earth Rat''' (жИКе≠Р, гБ§гБ°гБЃгБИгБ≠гАБгБЉгБ©гБЃгБ≠гБЪгБњгАБгБЉгБ©гБЃгБ≠гАБгБЉгБЧ, tsuchinoe-ne, bodo-no-nezumi, bodo-no-ze, boshi) is one element of the {{ill|Sexagenary Cycle Comprehensive|ja|Sexagenary cycle comprehensive|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sexagenary Cycle Comprehensive|qq=}}.

It is the 25th combination in the Sexagenary Cycle Comprehensive, preceded by {{ill|Ding Hai|ja|1=Yin Fire Pig|2=ja|дЄБдЇ•|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ding Hai|qq=}} and followed by {{ill|Ki Chou|ja|1=Yin Earth Ox|2=ja|еЈ±дЄС|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ki Chou|qq=}}. In the {{ill|Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|ja|йЩ∞йЩљдЇФи°МжАЭжГ≥|1=Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|1=Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|qq=}}, the {{ill|Wu|ja|жИК|1=Tsuchinoe (жИК)|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Wu|13=User:Immanuelle/Tsuchinoe (жИК)|qq=}} of the {{ill|Heavenly Stems|lt=Ten Heavenly Stems|ja|еНБеє≤|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Heavenly Stems|qq=}} represents yang earth, while the {{ill|Zi|ja|е≠Р|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Zi|qq=}} of the {{ill|Twelve Earthly Branches|1=Earthly Branches|lt=Twelve Earthly Branches|ja|еНБдЇМжФѓ|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Twelve Earthly Branches|13=User:Immanuelle/Earthly Branches|qq=}} represents yang water, and according to the principle of mutual overcoming ({{ill|S≈Нkoku|ja|зЫЄеЙЛ|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/S≈Нkoku|qq=}}; earth overcomes water).

