{{infobox Chinese|l=Yang Earth Rat|kanji=жИКе≠Р|romaji=tsuchinoe nezumi|onyomi=boshi|p=w√єz«Р|w=wu-tz≈≠|mi=uвБµвБµ ts…®|y=mou6 zi2|j=mou6 zi2|ci=m…Рu tsi|mc=m…Щu tsi|oc-bs=m…Щ tsi|qq=}} {{Sexagenary cycle comprehensive|qq=}} '''Yang Earth Rat''' (жИКе≠Р, гБ§гБ°гБЃгБИгБ≠гАБгБЉгБ©гБЃгБ≠гБЪгБњгАБгБЉгБ©гБЃгБ≠гАБгБЉгБЧ, tsuchinoe-ne, bodo-no-nezumi, bodo-no-ze, boshi) is one element of the {{ill|Sexagenary Cycle Comprehensive|ja|Sexagenary cycle comprehensive|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sexagenary Cycle Comprehensive|qq=}}.
It is the 25th combination in the Sexagenary Cycle Comprehensive, preceded by {{ill|Ding Hai|ja|1=Yin Fire Pig|2=ja|дЄБдЇ•|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ding Hai|qq=}} and followed by {{ill|Ki Chou|ja|1=Yin Earth Ox|2=ja|еЈ±дЄС|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ki Chou|qq=}}. In the {{ill|Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|ja|йЩ∞йЩљдЇФи°МжАЭжГ≥|1=Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|1=Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|qq=}}, the {{ill|Wu|ja|жИК|1=Tsuchinoe (жИК)|lt=Tsuchinoe (жИК)|2=ja|3=жИК|4=zh|5=жИК|1=Tsuchinoe (жИК)|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Wu|13=User:Immanuelle/Tsuchinoe (жИК)|qq=}} of the [[:en:Heavenly Stems|Ten Heavenly Stems]] represents yang earth, while the {{ill|Zi|ja|е≠Р|1=Rat (zodiac)|lt=Rat (е≠Р)|2=ja|3=е≠Р (еНБдЇМжФѓ)|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Zi|qq=}} of the [[:en:Earthly Branches|Twelve Earthly Branches]] represents yang water, and according to the principle of mutual overcoming ({{ill|S≈Нkoku|ja|зЫЄеЙЛ|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/S≈Нkoku|qq=}}; earth overcomes water).
==Pronunciation== PronounceYang Earth Rat
