It is the 25th combination in the Sexagenary Cycle Comprehensive, preceded by {{ill|Ding Hai|ja|1=Yin Fire Pig|2=ja|дЄБдЇ•|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ding Hai|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} and followed by {{ill|Ki Chou|ja|1=Yin Earth Ox|2=ja|еЈ±дЄС|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ki Chou|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}}. In the {{ill|Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|ja|йЩ∞йЩљдЇФи°МжАЭжГ≥|1=Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|1=Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|qq=}}, the {{ill|Wu|ja|жИК|1=Tsuchinoe (жИК)|lt=Tsuchinoe (жИК)|2=ja|3=жИК|4=zh|5=жИК|1=Tsuchinoe (жИК)|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Wu|13=User:Immanuelle/Tsuchinoe (жИК)|qq=}} of the [[:en:Heavenly Stems|Ten Heavenly Stems]] represents yang earth, while the [[:en:Rat (zodiac)|Rat (е≠Р)]] of the [[:en:Earthly Branches|Twelve Earthly Branches]] represents yang water, and according to the principle of mutual overcoming ({{ill|S≈Нkoku|ja|зЫЄеЙЛ|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/S≈Нkoku|qq=|ja_comment=fixed jawiki redirect|3=дЇФи°МжАЭжГ≥}}; earth overcomes water).
